  "detailed_description": "Super \"Mando\" needs your help to travel the city searching for what his wife asked him to buy urgently. The streets, the subway, the stores, everywhere full of crazy cars and jumping motorcycles. Ride a drone and dodge the obstacles to reach your goal. This is a retro plataformer game with 32 levels to jump and crush the traffic of the city, find cookies and hammers that will help you complete the levels, collect tokens to redeem them for lives and powerups.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145320/extras/95e5a2e98d679e125eb5b6b09336a65f.avif?t=1688429785\" width=400 height=150 /></span>",
